  </strong>
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <video autoplay="" class="bb_img" height="450" loop="" muted="" playsinline="" poster="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3435260/extras/1f8d5ed8080e94410ceb4f964504390f.poster.avif?t=1773679916" width="800">
