   </video>
  </span>
  I am afraid you have passed into the world beyond our own. Before you get there however, Death has offered to give you time to process your demise through means of some friendly competition.
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <img class="bb_img" height="190" src="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3435260/extras/01c90e8523c17f5c2aaa0b22e0709baf.avif" width="616"/>
  </span>
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  <strong>
   Engage in a game of Dice with the mysterious entity
  </strong>
  - collect new dice and their paired relics to warp your rolls into ever increasing layers of power and complexity. Bank your points to deal damage to your opponent, and pass before you push your luck too far or you'll lose it all!
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <img class="bb_img" height="190" src="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3435260/extras/5303c7a3b503dd91b768ebe2b3b575fa.avif" width="616"/>
